abstract: >-
  financial-analyst is a 14-tier-based multi-agent research workstation for
  A-share (Chinese stock market) single-stock deep-dive analysis. It combines
  25 specialized sub-agents (data fetchers, analysts, decision-makers,
  post-mortem introspector) with pluggable memory, FTS5-backed retrieval,
  multi-LLM provider routing (qwen / deepseek / openai / anthropic), and
  3-tier trust isolation for handling untrusted news / F10 sources.
